  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fd3ecde65e0933d4d8e78e24e9ae3820, type: 3}
  m_Name: IllTanYourHideFighterDialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  resourceName: I'll Tan Your Hide (Fighter)
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  description: 
  resourceDescriptionProfile: 
  automatic: 0
  repeatable: 0
  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Now that you have a basic weapon to deal with the bunnies around
      the camp, you can begin collecting ingredients for more powerful weapons and
      armor.


      Master Impassive has asked you to craft Initiates Leather Armor and a set of
      Copper Claws.'
    nextOption: How do I make those?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You will 5 Flax and 5 Leather for the armor.


      The Claws will require 2 Copper Ore and 1 Birch Lumber.'
    nextOption: Where do I get those?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Everything you need is here in the camp.


      Search the nearby rocks for Copper Ore.


      There is Flax near the crafting table.


      There should be a tree ready cut down behind Master Impassive.'
    nextOption: What about the leather?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You can get that from the bunnies.


      Talk to me again and I''ll teach you how to turn their skins into Leather and
      find the Flax, Birch Lumber, and Iron Ores.'
    nextOption: I really have to wear dead bunny skins?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Yep.


      Then bring me the Rabbit Hides, the Flax, the Birch Lumber, and the Iron Ores
      and I''ll teach you how to work that into weapons and armor.'
    nextOption: Are you sure about this?
  prerequisiteConditions: []
